## Creating Jobs

### Generate a Job

```bash
rails generate job ArticleNotification
```

**Creates:** `app/jobs/article_notification_job.rb`

### Basic Job Structure

```ruby
# app/jobs/article_notification_job.rb

class ArticleNotificationJob < ApplicationJob
  # Set queue name
  queue_as :default
  
  # Retry configuration
  retry_on StandardError, wait: 5.seconds, attempts: 3
  
  # Discard on certain errors (don't retry)
  discard_on ActiveJob::DeserializationError
  
  # Main job logic
  def perform(article_id)
    article = Article.find(article_id)
    
    # Send notifications to followers
    article.user.followers.each do |follower|
      ArticleMailer.new_article(follower, article).deliver_now
    end
  end
end
```

